{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-002", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·002.1", "text_original": "敦彼行葦，牛羊勿踐履。方苞方體，維葉泥泥。\n戚戚兄弟，莫遠具爾。或肆之筵，或授之几。", "text_normalized": "敦彼行葦，牛羊勿踐履。方苞方體，維葉泥泥。\n戚戚兄弟，莫遠具爾。或肆之筵，或授之几。", "notes": "行葦 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-002", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·002.2", "text_original": "肆筵設席，授几有緝御。或獻或酢，洗爵奠斝。\n醓醢以薦，或燔或炙。嘉殽脾臄，或歌或咢。", "text_normalized": "肆筵設席，授几有緝御。或獻或酢，洗爵奠斝。\n醓醢以薦，或燔或炙。嘉殽脾臄，或歌或咢。", "notes": "行葦 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-002", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·002.3", "text_original": "敦弓既堅，四鍭既鈞。舍矢既均，序賓以賢。\n敦弓既句，既挾四鍭。四鍭如樹，序賓以不侮。", "text_normalized": "敦弓既堅，四鍭既鈞。舍矢既均，序賓以賢。\n敦弓既句，既挾四鍭。四鍭如樹，序賓以不侮。", "notes": "行葦 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-002", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·002.4", "text_original": "曾孫維主，酒醴維醹。酌以大斗，以祈黃耇。\n黃耇台背，以引以翼，壽考維祺，以介景福。", "text_normalized": "曾孫維主，酒醴維醹。酌以大斗，以祈黃耇。\n黃耇台背，以引以翼，壽考維祺，以介景福。", "notes": "行葦 Chinese stanza 4."}
